# SinTrafico
SinTrafico API is a *Traffic Information System* service.
# Group Layers
**SinTrafico Layers API** enables to visualize traffic conditions in a map.

## Real Time Traffic Layer [/layers/traffic/x/y/z.format{?predict}]
Real time traffic layer updated every 15 minutes.

+ Parameters
    + x (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `X` coordinate of the TMS tile.
    + y (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `Y` coordinate of the TMS tile.
    + z (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `Z` zoom level of the TMS tile.
    + format (required, text, `png`) ... Format of the traffic layer png or json (vector tiles).
    + predict (optional, time, `2D15:00Z  Wednesday at 15 o'clock in UTC`) ... **n** D **hh**: **mm** Z . time in UTC where **n** is the day of week (Zero = Monday), **hh** left zero padded hours, and **mm** left zero padded minutes number. 

### Get layer [GET]
+ Request /layers/traffic/11/453/872.png (application/json)
        
+ Response 200 (image/png)
    
    + Header
    
            Content-Length: 14580053
        
    + Body
    
            {image data here}


