# Group Routing
## Routing [/routing?origin&{destination}]
A Routing service that uses real-time traffic information to provide the best route available.

+ Parameters
    + origin (required, text, `19.8523,-88.264`) ... Coordinates (lat,long) of the origin
    + destination (optional, text, `19.782,-88.822`) ... Coordinates (lat,long) of the destination, if it's not received, traffic info of the origin point will be provided.

### Retrieve a Route [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header

            X-My-Header: The Value

    + Body

            { "id": 2, "title": "Pick-up posters from post-office" }


